snippet.title: THE PATHLESS | Gameplay Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Creative Director Matt Nava talks through what to expect when you dive into the world of The Pathless. Coming later this year to PS5, PS4, and Epic Games Store. Wishlist now: https://www.epicgames.com/store/en-US/product/the-pathless/home

Developed by GIANT SQUID. Published by Annapurna Interactive.
